snippet.textDisplay:
So are we going to ignore the fact that this is a false advertisement? They introduce Maya as a "customizable character" not as a permanent customization. They tell you that after you spent your money on the Battle pass. And you can't redo your choices on the outfit after you confirm them, imagine all the people that bought it just to play with the customization and realize is a 1 time only. If you're reading this keep in mind that it'll probably be the same for the other skins too where you choose Shadow or Ghost. So all the people that bought the battle pass got scammed. They show skins with styles and you'll only be getting half of what you paid for. So RIP to those extra styles for every S2C2 skins. This was a really stupid idea of making stuff permanent and promote it as "customizable and more".

For example i like both Midas style Shadow and Ghost but if i choose Shadow i won't be able to have his other style which is also nice looking. So technically it shows it has 2 styles but in reality you can only get 1 of the 2 styles for something YOU PAID FOR! This is really misleading and unfair they really need to do something about this ASAP, because i know im not the only one that brought the battle pass for the "customizations and extra styles" and we are getting half of everything.
